717603f.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 63rd Street
717603f.text:
1896-1890 Broadway, at the S.E. corner of 63rd Street. This
building will stand in 1934.
1918.
nift of E. M. Jenks.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
